data.value: Resolve player effects that occur during Cleanup Phase Characters with Dazed token remove all damage, conditions, and the dazed token. Flip to injured side. Crisis Team characters without activated tokens advance Small

Set up game as instructed in the Ultron Ultimate Encounter rule book
It is important you fully understand the rules of the encounter before you start using the App
You will not need the Ultron character card, or the Score and Round counter
Perform the Power Phase and then click the button to start
